snippet.title: Weaponeer: VoxPop Games Edition
snippet.description:
A NEW ADVENTURE...MADE FOR VOXPOPGAMES!!!

WISHLIST TODAY : https://rb.gy/6e8bff

WEAPONEER: VoxPop Games Edition
Control your character with two buttons and fight your way through 60+ levels of retro platforming that introduce new original content. You wield your sword and try to make your way back home.

Proceeds from the purchase of this title will go directly to the AbleGamers charity organization! #SoEVERYONECanGame

#EveryVoiceMatters
